apne ( ours ) is a 2007 indian hindi sports drama film directed by anil sharma . it is the first and one of the three films to feature real life father and sons dharmendra , sunny deol and bobby deol together . sunny and bobby had worked together before in dillagi and dharmendra and sunny had also appeared together in &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( 1986 ) and &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( 1993 ) . kiron kher , shilpa shetty and katrina kaif play the female leads . the film opened to an excellent response across india and emerged as a hit overseas as well . dharmendra plays the role of a disgraced &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; baldev chaudhary who tries to wash a stain in his boxing career through his sons angad and karan ( sunny & bobby deol ) . dharmendra had earlier played the role of a boxer in the film main &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( 1982 ) . footage from that film is used as flashback scenes in this film to show baldev 's career as a boxer .